General Information

A light oil, rich in Vitamin E, which penetrates easily into the skin and is very suitable for oily and combination skin types. Suitable for face and body. Jojoba oil has the longest shelf life of all the carrier oils as it is a liquid wax and does not oxidise.

Warnings

STORE BELOW 30C. NOT TO BE TAKEN ORALLY. KEEP OUT OF REACH OF CHILDREN.

Ingredients

Simmondsia chinensis seed fixed oil 1ml/mL

Directions

Adult: For the symptomatic relief of the symptoms of eczema and relief of the effects of Psoriases on the skin: apply directly to the affected area as required.
